702016f-a.title: Bronx: Waring Avenue - Woodhull Avenue
702016f-a.text:
Waring Avene, adjoining the S.W. corner of Woodhull Avenue (location of house), showing an old farm house. The view is eastward from Eastchester Road.
May 11, 1938.
P.L. Sperr
